high_descs: Turn and walk to face the sink.
Pick up the plate that is on the right side of the sink.
Turn left and walk over to face the stove and microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the plate inside, close the door and set the microwave to run for three seconds, then open the door, take the plate out and close the door again
Turn around and walk to the brown shelf in the right-hand back-corner of the room.
Place the plate on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed-up plate on the shelf.

high_descs: Go to the sink to your left.
Pick up the plate that's in the sink.
Go the the microwave to your right.
Put the plate in the microwave, then take it out.
Turn around and go to the shelf on your right.
Put the plate on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the plate from the sink onto the shelf.

high_descs: Turn right, walk a few steps, and then turn left to face the sink.
Pick up the plate in the sink.
Turn left, walk towards the wall, and then turn right to face the stove.
Place the plate in the microwave above the stove to heat it.
Turn around, walk a little a head, turn right, and then walk ahead to find the wooden shelf next to the wall.
Place the plate on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated plate on the shelf.
